	<string>We use notifications to keep you updated with important information.</string>
	<key>NSLocationWhenInUseUsageDescription</key>
	<string>We need access to your location to test geofencing features.</string>
	<key>NSLocationAlwaysAndWhenInUseUsageDescription</key>
	<string>We need access to your location even when the app is in the background to monitor geofences and send you location-based notifications.</string>
	<key>NSLocationAlwaysUsageDescription</key>
	<string>We need access to your location even when the app is in the background to monitor geofences.</string>
